setEditArrowKeys

public void setEditArrowKeys(int x)
Defines the arrow keys that will be used by the editor for editing. Others that are not defined will allow for navigating from cell to cell.
Need to OR "|" : UP, DOWN, LEFT, RIGHT.

setDisabledArrowKeys

public void setDisabledArrowKeys(int x)
Deprecated. Use setEditArrowKeys to define keys that are permitted

Defines the arrow keys that are to be ignored.
Need to OR, UP, DOWN, LEFT, RIGHT.
